    public class OIDGeneric
extends Object
    Generic Class for treatment of some attributes of certificates of ICP-BRASIL, for: Individual (Pessoa Física) of the Business Entity (Pessoa Jurídica) and Equipment. In accordance with the standards defined in DOC-ICP-04 v2.0 dated 04/18/2006.
